# Curated visual evidence under baseline/ and react/ (screenshots, fingerprints,
# manifests) IS committed — this file does NOT ignore it. It ONLY excludes the
# Playwright RUNTIME output that `npm run e2e` regenerates and that must never be
# committed as evidence (F-SEC-01, CWE-532/CWE-200): the per-phase output/
# folder (videos/traces/last-run) and the generated HTML report/. This is the
# targeted opposite of the legacy "ignore the whole directory" trick — it keeps
# the curated evidence tracked while keeping regenerated, potentially
# credential-bearing runtime files out of version control.
*/output/
report/
